data.description: FARM LIVING! Move right into the country lifestyle with a seasonal creek, chicken coop, fenced area for small animals and lots of space to create. The property  is completely fenced and gated and mostly level. The property is 3.65 acres and it features amazing views . The well kept 3/2 manufactured home with permanent foundation has a  large covered deck and a 180 sq ft bonus room with its own covered deck that overlooks the creek. The second building is used as an art studio and the power is connected, plumbing is there and needs to be connected. The main home features vaulted ceilings in the living room, updated appliances &  flooring, ceiling fans and newer monitor heater. Siding and windows were replaced 5 years ago. Other interesting items are the large container/shop. Oversized pump house with loads of extra storage. Pump and piping were replaced recently. Fenced garden area. oversized well built chicken coop and several fruit trees in a fenced yard. NOTE:The accuracy of the information provided is deemed reliable but is not guaranteed; all sizes, measurements, square footage, and descriptions are approximate, are subject  to change and should be independently verified.
